'''Marc Wendt''' is an archivist for [[Lucas Licensing]], and an actor who played [[Ichi-Tan Micoda]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]. As a musician, Wendt has worked extensively in the fields of songwriting, performance, and recording.

